chat.msg: hola, you ready?
Yes.
awesome! i'm at the starting point, a twig to my left, islands and animals around
where to first?
You would want to go in a straight direction towards the twig, from there cross over the water and you'll see a giraffe
got it, moving past the twig and i see the giraffe now, cool! what's the next step?
Once you cross over and see the giraffe, there are 2 big rocks you can walk across to the side in which you'd see a elephant to your left
awesome, crossing the rocks and wohoo, there's the elephant
where to now?
Go right. You should see a big black rock watch for the alligator. You would need to cross over the water where the alligator is
yeesh! alligator crossed, safely
where do i head next?

You should see a tree on the right and frog on the left go. In front of the frog to the left you'd see 2 big gray rocks and a black on used as a stepping stone across the water. You'll run into a parrot in the tree.
rocks passed, hello mr
parrot! where to from here?
go around the tree to the right. You should see a limb that takes you across the water. There is a tiger on the left side. Watch out!
oh my! tiger spotted! safely across the water though, what's up next?
Keep walk straight and cross over the water and you'd see a map on the other side
map spotted! should i cross to it?
Yes, cross to it
done! map crossed
what's up next?
hey there, estas listo?
hello
perfect! let's start where the white dog is. go few steps left, passing below a wooden bench, then cross that trail towards the florist stand
but don't reach it yet, just make a quick u-turn to your left, cross the trail again and head back towards our furry friend. got it?
What's next
alright, next you cross over the branch, going south, till you spot another white dog chilling by a checkered picnic blanket
you there yet?
Found the white dog and picnic blanket
nice job! now stride over the picnic blanket, touch the bowl of berries and keep moving west
look out for a wooden branch
Touched the berries and see the wooden branch. Whats next
great! now cross that river using the wooden branch, heading up north
Done, whats next
once you've crossed, avoid the green bush
instead, go circle it from the right till you can see the florist stand. you're doing great!
Went on around the bush and can see the florist stand. What's next?
cool, now let's take a left turn, heading west, and go below that florist stand
you'll see a big bridge with two cyclists. keep going past it
Passed the cyclist. How fun! What's next?
you're doing amazing! just past the bridge, you should see two elderly people reading newspapers on a bench
can you spot them?
I see them
awesome! now, make a small move to the south, just between our newspaper-loving folks and another wooden branch, towards a green bush next to the branch's end
I see the branch with the bush. What's next?
great going! now travel east, stick to the path between the branch and that bush
What's next
you're almost there! just a few steps further east and you'll find a young brown deer
that's your final stop for now - go find our deer friend!
How adorable. Found the deer.
ha! awesome, knew you'd love it
well done on the navigation, you were stellar!
What's next
you reached the end, well done! let's just chill with the deer
you did awesome!
hola, q tal? ready to start?
Yes
cool! standing at our tent, facing south
we got a dog to our left side by the fire and a red mushroom to our right. which way to go?
Go straight, You're going to go around the front of the dog then loop around the back of the fire
gotcha! pup's to our left, fire's on the right
hey, i see a blue car straight ahead. where to next?
Walk passed the front of the red mushroom headed towards the car but don't go to far. Make a U turn and you'll see a green bush on the left in front of the blue car
alright, blue car behind us, facing the green bush now
yeap, see a telescope in the distance, is that where we're headed?
Yes, Head towards where the blue telescope is. You're going to walk between the telescope on the right and a bush on the left
okay, between the telescope & bush now
You'll see a trail take that trail going right and you'll see a house walk towards the house
sweet, walking towards the house now
*finished* thanks bud!
hola, you ready?
Yes
awesome! start by heading under the first palm tree to your southwest. next, take a right, pass the second tree and then sharp left
keep going straight southwards. easy peasy, right?
Ok. whats next
next, you should see a brown puppy
make a slight left past it and then jolt back to the south. just follow those puppies eyes, buddy!
Seen the brown puppy, What
sweet! now, spot a big rock to your left and a small one on your right. walk right in between those two
head straight towards that beautiful blue of the ocean. excited, eh?
The ocean is very blue. Whats next
get ready to meet a crabby friend! enter the water, look for a big red crab, and turn right - that's westwards
keep following the big rock. let's swim!
See the big red crab. What's next
awesome! keep going west until you hit a medium rock
Be careful not to bump into it! on seeing a shark, make a sharp right. don't let jaws spook anymore!
Ooohh Shark! Where to now
ha! gotcha there! now, steer back to land, squeezing between that rock and a multicolored ball
then, it's north-bound matey!
In between the ball and rock. What's next
great! now, let's go a bit northwest, passing between a red tent on your left and a big speaker on your right
I've passed the red tent. What's next
perfect! now just circle round the tent like a ninja then head south, but don’t get wet! stop at the sea shore
I'm at the sea shore. What's next
awesome! now turn right, heading west, and go under the red kayak
enjoy the shade!
Im under the kayak. Where to now
all right my friend! turn right again, move north along the kayak until you reach a cute small green bush
you've made it! how's that for an adventure?
Cool. Thanks
you're welcome! that was fun, wasn't it? ready for another round?
